			mSpellDescriptions.add(new SpellDescriptionRecord("Pheromones", "This spell gives the caster a strong emotional control over those of the opposite sex. ( 50% + 2% per level of caster )  The victim does NOT get a Saving throw against this spell.  The emotions let loose are LUST & LOVE.  The problem is that it is a area spell 5' X Level, and all those of the opposite sex in that area are going to be affected.  The affect this spell has on the same sex is a little different, the are enraged by the caster on site and may well attack with little or no provication.  A strong perfume, anti-magic or a strong wind will dissipitate this spell and give those affected a 20% chance to regain their composure.", new Pair("Range", "5' X Level of Caster"), new Pair("Duration", "10 Minutes X Level of Caster  Note :  this spell cannot just be turned off like most spells, it must run it's course."))); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$ //$NON-NLS-3$ //$NON-NLS-4$ //$NON-NLS-5$ //$NON-NLS-6$
